<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Enhanced Home Page</title>
    <style>
        /* General styling */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #f5f7fa, #c3cfe2);
            color: #333;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .header button {
            padding: 10px 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: white;
            background-color: #e74c3c;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .header button:hover {
            background-color: #c0392b;
        }

        .dark-mode-btn {
            background-color: #3498db;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }

        .main-content {
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .content-box {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: calc(50% - 20px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .content-box h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .content-box p {
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .profile-card {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .profile-card img {
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .profile-card h3 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .contact-section {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .contact-section h2 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .contact-section form input,
        .contact-section form textarea {
            width: calc(100% - 20px);
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .contact-section form button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #2ecc71;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .contact-section form button:hover {
            background-color: #27ae60;
        }

        .quick-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .quick-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            background-color: #8e44ad;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .quick-links a:hover {
            background-color: #732d91;
        }

        /* Dark mode styles */
        .dark-mode {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: #ecf0f1;
        }

        .dark-mode .header {
            background-color: #1c2833;
        }

        .dark-mode .content-box,
        .dark-mode .profile-card,
        .dark-mode .contact-section {
            background-color: #34495e;
            color: #ecf0f1;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to the Enhanced Home Page</h1>
        <div>
            <button onclick="logout()">Logout</button>
            <button onclick="changePassword()">Change Password</button>
            <button class="dark-mode-btn" onclick="toggleDarkMode()">Toggle Dark Mode</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main-content">
        <!-- User Profile -->
        <div class="profile-card">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="User Profile">
            <h3>John Doe</h3>
            <p>Frontend Developer</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Node.js Section -->
        <div class="content-box">
            <h2>Node.js</h2>
            <p>Node.js is a runtime environment that allows developers to run JavaScript on the server side. It is fast,
                scalable, and widely used in web development for building server-side applications.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- MongoDB Section -->
        <div class="content-box">
            <h2>MongoDB</h2>
            <p>MongoDB is a NoSQL database that stores data in a flexible, JSON-like format. It is popular for its
                scalability and ease of integration with modern applications.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Express.js Section -->
        <div class="content-box">
            <h2>Express.js</h2>
            <p>Express.js is a web application framework for Node.js, providing a robust set of features to develop web
                and mobile applications. It simplifies routing, middleware, and handling requests and responses.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Tailwind CSS Section -->
        <div class="content-box">
            <h2>Tailwind CSS</h2>
            <p>Tailwind CSS is a utility-first CSS framework that provides low-level building blocks for rapid UI
                development. It is highly customizable and works seamlessly with modern frameworks.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- React.js Section -->
        <div class="content-box">
            <h2>React.js</h2>
            <p>React.js is a JavaScript library for building user interfaces. It uses a component-based architecture and
                is widely used for building interactive and dynamic front-end applications.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact Us Section -->
   

    <!-- Quick Links -->
    <div class="quick-links">
        <a href="#node">Node.js</a>
        <a href="#mongodb">MongoDB</a>
        <a href="#express">Express.js</a>
        <a href="#tailwind">Tailwind CSS</a>
        <a href="#react">React.js</a>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Logout function
        function logout() {
            alert("You have been logged out!");
            window.location.href = "login";
        }

        // Change Password function
        function changePassword() {
            alert("Redirecting to the Change Password page...");
            window.location.href = "/api/changePassword";
        }

        // Dark Mode Toggle
        function toggleDarkMode() {
            document.body.classList.toggle("dark-mode");
        }
    </script>
</body>

</html>
